%h2 The only step to start writing

%p.lead
  Write The Scene is 2-person chat game where you improvise a screenplay with your partner.
  %br
  Creativity is your only limitation.


= form_tag start_path do |f|
  = label_tag :username, 'Who do you want to be?'
  .input-append
    = text_field_tag :username
    - if @scene
      = hidden_field_tag :scene_id, @scene.id
      = submit_tag 'Join the Scene!', class: 'btn'
    - else
      = submit_tag 'Start the Scene!', class: 'btn'
